{"tid":1746412,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】【又係元朗國】區選文宣前哨戰","createTime":"2019-11-22T17:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T10:23:51.000Z","uid":255486,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d03d6e674aa05048ebc6a7f51cf14f050fcf0755","tid":1746412,"uid":255486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:43:50.000Z","msg":"借ac代手足po<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/23/003817_1e0e516f4a9f3d6a87a6e785bd27c2e8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F23%2F003817_1e0e516f4a9f3d6a87a6e785bd27c2e8.jpeg&h=92d34046&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pk4Monv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpk4Monv.jpg&h=826aa62f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vSpHF9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvSpHF9b.jpg&h=386ac862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n距離區選淨番一日乍，大家嘅親朋戚友知道自己咩選區有咩候選人可以揀未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果未&hellip;咁就快啲學下元朗文宣手足喇。<br />\n<br />\n1. 大大塊牆放哂當區候選人大頭相，行過路過冇藉口唔知唔信睇唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(因為放哂所有人，所以冇扺觸任何選舉條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n2. 列出哂當區投票站嘅地點同地址，唔熟路都可以搭的士，冇藉口話唔識去啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(選舉網頁有齊，印落黎乍)<br />\n3. 文宣手足不停提街坊一定要投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地原來仲自製左一張區選poster，講返上屆區選元朗區有過半選民冇投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n懶成咁，唔怪得輸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 唔少街坊都樂意停低一兩分鐘去討論政事，氣氛唔錯(好撚葡萄元朗有啲咁nice嘅街坊)<br />\n<br />\n區選重點從來唔係比泛民嬴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而係要令保皇偽獨立輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有，比機會新世代去改變香港，重建香港。畢竟，未來係屬於年輕嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">11。24</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">朝早七點半全民投票</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">踢走保皇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M48UxfS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM48UxfS.jpg&h=6ebf4c30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"717a128778ad68a94d335f7d523756ea3ba15ba7","tid":1746412,"uid":255486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:44:23.000Z","msg":"1124 七點半投票喇"},{"pid":"70ce2a8bf767b0f8cdf587a56b834710d6941501","tid":1746412,"uid":255486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:44:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"708aa9eebd9bd30c063567265911122ebcafef34","tid":1746412,"uid":255486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:46:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9c2da6f70ddb1ff2ca92154091701f9d44c62d7c","tid":1746412,"uid":8049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:48:17.000Z","msg":"幫推 記得投票!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358be0ae50139bba74748e221a1ca6d239902007","tid":1746412,"uid":149435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:48:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"570980390b8cb72c196bdcf7aa2d82f90f572783","tid":1746412,"uid":213793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T18:04:30.000Z","msg":"文宣好靚!! 又清楚又易睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝元朗文宣巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其它區不要太羨慕，但都要去投票阿!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1586752679313260769f7029d9f7824f44069ef","tid":1746412,"uid":255486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T18:11:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"687b2a735ca3b86c504b50294a43c33953122781","tid":1746412,"uid":129466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:23:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}